        "content": "<p>I've been scrolling through the <a href=\"https://crates.io/crates?sort=downloads\">most downloaded</a> page of <a href=\"https://crates.io\">https://crates.io</a>, and started working on a few libs in my free time to fill out our ecosystem. The first one I've finished is <a href=\"https://github.com/smores56/roc-semver\">roc-semver</a>, an implementation of <a href=\"https://semver.org/\">semver 2.0.0</a> in Roc.</p>\n<p>Many thanks to the <a href=\"https://rust-lang.org\">Rust</a> implementation <a href=\"https://github.com/dtolnay/semver\">here</a> by David Tolnay. I'm gonna finish up testing and docs tomorrow and then publish a release when that's finished.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Elm\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">version</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Parse</span><span class=\"nf\">.</span><span class=\"nv\">semver</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"1.2.3-alpha.beta+build--\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"nv\">expect</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nv\">version</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Ok</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nv\">major</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nv\">minor</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nv\">patch</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nv\">preRelease</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s\">\"alpha\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"beta\"</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nv\">build</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s\">\"build--\"</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
